
#  Create a webhook 
#  ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
#  WEBHOOK SETUP STEPS: 
#  ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

01. Open slack in your web browser

02. Open a new web browser tab 

03. Type   api.slack.com

04. Click [YOUR APPS] (top right)

05. Create a New App [FROM SCRATCH]

06. Name the app

07. Select a workspace 

08. Press [Create app]

09. Click incoming webhooks (left hand panel)

10. Move the slider button to [ON] if it is off

11. [ADD NEW WEBHHOOK] bottom of the screen - Select a channel where you want your messages to appear

12. Press allow 

13. Scroll to the bottom of the screen

14. [Copy] the webhook, open notepad++ and paste in the result

15. Keep a copy of the webhook

